5130401.tips: In front of a balloon fishing booth, a kid with blonde hair gets into an argument with the crowd over someone cutting in line. Seeing you with your weapon at hand, he seems to take you for an accomplice of another group about to get involved...
5130401.name: Ruckus at the Booth

5130402.tips: Several children surround a patrol AGI Mecha, blocking its path and roaring with laughter at its repeated warnings. Just as you go over to stop them, you see the AGI Mecha's display turn red. Uh-oh, look out!
5130402.name: A Senseless Calamity

5130403.tips:
You go with the flow of the crowd, but it's feeling increasingly tight. Suddenly, you sense a change in the movement of the tourists up ahead. Now, the people at the front are rushing behind you.
"Run!! An AGI Mecha has started attacking people out of nowhere!"
5130403.name: AGI Mecha Crisis

5130404.tips: Having decided to camp in the wilderness, you set up simple traps using the crafting skills you learned from an old hunter. Before long, you hear the cry of an animal. As the cries grow louder, however, your prey seems to be breaking free...
5130404.name: A Beast Stirs

5130405.tips:
"Help me! A wild animal attacked me!"
You rush toward the calls for help and discover a youth leaning weakly against a tree marred with claw marks. Sensing you approach, the youth looks up, revealing a deranged smile. Careful...!
5130405.name: S.O.S.

5130406.tips:
A villager from a nameless island looks at the lake and sees a pair of red eyes reflected on its surface.
"Huh? You have red eyes too?"
5130406.name: Ghost Story

5130407.tips: In the shadows out of sight, a rustling sound echoes through the empty room. Shackles and chains cast shadows on the wall, on the verge of breaking.
5130407.name: Shadows in the Dark

5130408.tips:
"Give me back my wallet!"
"YOUR wallet? This is clearly MY wallet!"
Uh-oh, looks like a fight's about to start. Stop them before things get ugly!
5130408.name: Opportunistic Acquisition

5130409.tips: A sudden breeze sweeps through the silent grove, and the bushes begin to tremble. What's in there?!
5130409.name: Vigilance

5130410.tips:
Exhausted after the festivities, you follow the crowd off the streets. Not paying attention to the direction of the flow, you suddenly find yourself out of the city.
Too tired to turn back, you figure that camping outside for the night isn't a bad idea. Still, you may want to make sure the area's safe first.
5130410.name: Wild Camping

5130411.tips: Mentally and physically worn out from the day's hustle and bustle, you prepare to make camp in the forest. Just then, your stomach growls, signaling the need for food. Better get hunting!
5130411.name: Access to Food

5130412.tips: A group of people, their faces covered, look at you with malice in their eyes. Before you can figure out why, they're already charging at you.
5130412.name: A Malevolent Look

5130413.tips: A young man with a flippant demeanor is promoting Neuhansa-made AGI Mecha to tourists. Checking them over, you're not sure they were come by honestly. Following your gaze, the young man drops the smile and invites you to his place to "sit a while."
5130413.name: The Salesman

5130414.tips: Out on the streets bustling with festivities, a narrow, dimly-lit alley catches your attentionâ€”mostly because you're the only one who seems to see it. Stepping into it, you feel as though you've barged into someone's private domain, as if you've bored through the "membrane" of reality.
5130414.name: False Realm

5130415.tips: A viscous liquid giving off an unsettling odor formed a tether-like line. It's up to you to figure out what this thing is.
5130415.name: Trail of Filth

5130416.tips: In the festival procession, you run into a young man acting strangely. Speaking words you can't understand, he launches an attack at you.
5130416.name: Strange Person

5130417.tips:
In the desolate forest depths, you see a frail youth on the ground by the lake. Strange as it is, you don't hesitate to go over to help.
After propping him up, you see a pair of scarlet eyes watching you...
5130417.name: Deep in the Woods
